  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't-- that didn't happen the roundup yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But later on, interestingly, that will play a part in my mother's situation and also that they, indeed, entered one of these houses, with my father.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were able to somehow get those papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the story goes on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was watching it from the first floor balcony.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really much conversation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just said that we should be together and try to-- not to lose sight of each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when we were going out in the streets, herds of people, hundreds, we were marching down on the street, followed by Arrow Cross and German uniformed people, who, who were guiding that nobody could step out and, and, and sneak away from whatever the destination point was where we were going.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we arrived to that racetrack--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--thousands of people were already herded up there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] again, the little needs of, of getting to a bathroom or a toilet, it was not.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were standing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then people started to urinate, just next to each other, and the bowels and, and degradation of human dignity started to appear on the scene.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was just an uncontrolled, big mess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were herded out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just like--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the uniformed people who, who came into the building and took us away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no question of resistance that we wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no question, none of us had anything to resist with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have arm, we didn't have the know-how, and we didn't have the guts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were just lambs herded away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had probably no more than a blanket, a little food, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] nothing else, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
